description:
With a Nintendo Switch Online + Expansion Pack membership, you can access the Nintendo 64™ – Nintendo Switch Online: MATURE 17+ collection of games. 
 
For the first time ever, you can play these select classic games online and use voice chat via the Nintendo Switch Online smartphone app*. Play at home or on the go, create suspend points for each game to save your progress, and even play online with voice chat via the Nintendo Switch Online smartphone app.

Multiplayer Requirements:
 
• Online: Players must have their own Nintendo Switch system with an active Nintendo Switch Online + Expansion Pack membership.
• Local multiplayer: One Nintendo Switch Online + Expansion Pack active membership and additional accessories (controllers) may be required.
name: Nintendo 64™ – Nintendo Switch Online: MATURE 17+
